squidpony.squidmath

Class MersenneTwister

  • java.lang.Object
    • squidpony.squidmath.MersenneTwister
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, RandomnessSource
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class MersenneTwister
extends Object
implements RandomnessSource
    RandomnessSource using Mersenne Twister algorithm (not recommended).
    Uses the Mersenne Twister algorithm to provide results with a longer period. Mersenne Twister has known statistical vulnerabilities, however, and this implementation is incredibly slow, which is why it is deprecated. You should use LongPeriodRNG for most of the cases that MersenneTwister would be good at in theory, or IsaacRNG for cases that need an extremely large period and cryptographic-like properties.
    Author:
    Daniel Dyer (Java Port), Makoto Matsumoto and Takuji Nishimura (original C version), Eben Howard - http://squidpony.com - howard@squidpony.com, Lewis Potter
